https://links.kukufm.com/C893Y3
show.description: A struggling young man is suddenly transported into his favorite crime novel — and reborn as its legendary detective. When a dancer is murdered at the Phoenix Dance Hall, a chilling link to an unsolved case from six years ago emerges. Now, armed with fiction’s brilliance and real stakes, he must crack the mystery before the past strikes again.
